 13, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNarrate to people only what they can understand. Do you want them to deny Allah and his messenger?\u201d Abu Hisham said, \u201cI never narrated anything people did not understand but that it led them astray.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u2019\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34790,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/24\/ibn-abbas-dhikr-allahi-akbar\/","url_meta":{"origin":22548,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Dhikr: Remembrance of Allah is the greatest deed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Antarah reported: I asked Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWhich deed is best?\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cThe remembrance of Allah is greatest, (29:45). No people sit in a house, in which they are occupied with the Book of Allah among them and they study it together, except\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33624,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/ibn-abbas-mothers-best-deed\/","url_meta":{"origin":22548,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Mothers: Good to mothers best deed to draw near to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ata\u2019 ibn Yasar reported: A man came to Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and he said, \u201cI proposed to a woman and she refused to marry me. Another man proposed to her and she was happy to marry him. I became jealous and I killed her. Is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34966,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/17\/aishah-humility-deathbed\/","url_meta":{"origin":22548,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Death: Aisha\u2019s Godfearing humility on her deathbed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Mulaykah reported: Ibn Abbas asked permission to see Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, before her death while she was overcome with suffering. Aisha said, \u201cI am afraid he will praise me.\u201d It was said, \u201cHe is the cousin of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33402,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/09\/ibn-abbas-knowledge-lost\/","url_meta":{"origin":22548,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Death: This is how Islamic knowledge is lost","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Zuhri reported: When they lowered Zayd ibn Thabit, may Allah be pleased with him, into his grave, Ibn Abbas said, \u201cWhoever would like to see how knowledge is lost, this here is the loss of knowledge.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 18053 \u0639\